{
  "script_id": "pigeonhole",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "pigeonhole",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pigeonhole/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.35,
      "size": 21600,
      "text": "有13只鸽子，要飞回12个巢里。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pigeonhole",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pigeonhole/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "不管它们怎么飞，总会有一个巢里挤进了至少两只鸽子。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pigeonhole",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pigeonhole/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.45,
      "size": 23184,
      "text": "不信你可以试，怎么摆都躲不开这个结果。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pigeonhole",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pigeonhole/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.81,
      "size": 28944,
      "text": "这个听起来理所当然的事实，正是著名的鸽巢原理。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pigeonhole",
      "section_id": "principle",
      "line_id": "prin-1",
      "filename": "principle-prin-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pigeonhole/xiaoxiao/principle-prin-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.0,
      "size": 31968,
      "text": "如果物品比抽屉多，那么必有某个抽屉里不止一个物品。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pigeonhole",
      "section_id": "principle",
      "line_id": "prin-2",
      "filename": "principle-prin-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pigeonhole/xiaoxiao/principle-prin-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.31,
      "size": 37008,
      "text": "更精确地说，必有某个抽屉至少装了 n 除以 m 向上取整那么多。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pigeonhole",
      "section_id": "principle",
      "line_id": "prin-3",
      "filename": "principle-prin-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pigeonhole/xiaoxiao/principle-prin-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.42,
      "size": 38736,
      "text": "13除以12向上取整是2，所以必有一巢至少两只，躲也躲不掉。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pigeonhole",
      "section_id": "general",
      "line_id": "gen-1",
      "filename": "general-gen-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pigeonhole/xiaoxiao/general-gen-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.69,
      "size": 43056,
      "text": "把它推广开来：n 加 1 个物品放进 n 个抽屉，必有一个抽屉装了两个以上。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pigeonhole",
      "section_id": "general",
      "line_id": "gen-2",
      "filename": "general-gen-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pigeonhole/xiaoxiao/general-gen-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 30960,
      "text": "物品越多、抽屉越少，被迫挤在一起的数量就越大。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pigeonhole",
      "section_id": "general",
      "line_id": "gen-3",
      "filename": "general-gen-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pigeonhole/xiaoxiao/general-gen-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "这条简单的原理，是组合数学里最锋利的证明工具之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pigeonhole",
      "section_id": "apply",
      "line_id": "app-1",
      "filename": "apply-app-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pigeonhole/xiaoxiao/apply-app-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "任意13个人里，必有两人生日在同一个月，因为月份只有12个。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pigeonhole",
      "section_id": "apply",
      "line_id": "app-2",
      "filename": "apply-app-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pigeonhole/xiaoxiao/apply-app-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.65,
      "size": 42480,
      "text": "一场聚会上，总有两个人握手的次数恰好相同，这也是鸽巢原理在起作用。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pigeonhole",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pigeonhole/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "试着调大鸽子数、调小巢数，看那些被高亮的拥挤巢穴。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pigeonhole",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pigeonhole/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.05,
      "size": 32832,
      "text": "只要鸽子多于巢，无论怎样随机分配，碰撞都必然出现。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pigeonhole",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pigeonhole/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "鸽巢原理说：物品多于抽屉，必有抽屉不止一个物品。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pigeonhole",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pigeonhole/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25200,
      "text": "简单的计数背后，是数学最迷人的必然性。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pigeonhole",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pigeonhole/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "愿你从此看见生活里藏着的抽屉，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 34.44,
  "total_size": 551232
}